(180, 1, '2016-02-02 03:37:57', '2016-02-02 03:37:57', '<strong>About University</strong>\r\nJiwaji University is a public affiliating university situated in Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh. Named after Jivajirao Scindia this university affiliates institutes of higher learning in six districts with more than 300 affiliate colleges. These colleges impart education upto  postgraduate level of study and some of these institutes are also recognized research centers . This university offers graduate and post graduate courses of study in faculties of arts&humanities, commerce, science, environment, education, science&technology, management, computer science&application and law .The most special department of this university is SOS in Neuroscience which conducts India''s only Department of Biotechnology-sponsored neuroscience teaching program at university level. Another distinctive feature of this university is its self supporting programs and need and job oriented courses of study. \r\n\r\nJiwaji University is a public affiliating university situated in Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh. \r\n\r\nEstablished In : 1964\r\nAffiliated To : UGC\r\nWebsite : <a href="http://www.jiwaji.edu/" target="_blank">http://www.jiwaji.edu/</a>\r\nAddress : Jiwaji University Gwalior (M.P.), India Ph: +91 751 2442712 Fax No.: +91 751 2341768\r\n', 'Jiwaji University Gwalior', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'jiwaji-university-gwalior', '', '', '2016-02-15 21:11:59', '2016-02-15 21:11:59', '', 0, 'http://www.mpinformation.com/?p=180', 0, 'post', '', 0),
