"]<img src="http://www.mpinformation.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/tigra-dam.jpg" alt="Tigra Dam" width="700" height="400" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-262" />Tigra Dam[/caption]\r\n\r\nTigra Dam is situated about 23 km from the city. The dam is huge and you will love the sight of migratory birds swimming in the water. Boating facilities are available here. This beautiful picnic spot is a perfect place to relax.\r\n', 'TOP 5 Attraction Place in Gwalior', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '303-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-10 02:38:39', '2016-02-10 02:38:39', '', 303, 'http://www.mpinformation.com/303-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
