(383, 1, '2016-02-11 22:32:50', '2016-02-11 22:32:50', '<h3>History</h3>\r\nIIM Indore, which came into existence in 1996, was established as the sixth Indian Institute of Management after<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IIM_Calcutta" title="IIM Calcutta"  target="_blank">IIM Calcutta</a>(1961),<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IIM_Ahmedabad" title="IIM Ahmedabad" target="_blank">IIM Ahmedabad</a>(1963),<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IIM_Bangalore" title="IIM Bangalore" target="_blank">IIM Bangalore</a>(1972),<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IIM_Lucknow" title="IIM Lucknow" target="_blank">IIM Lucknow</a>(1984) and<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IIM_Kozhikode" title="IIM Kozhikode" target="_blank">IIM Kozhikode</a>(1996).The institute was the youngest among the IIM''s until 2008, when<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IIM_Shillong" title="IIM Shillong" target="_blank">IIM Shillong</a>was instituted.\r\n\r\n<h3>Academics</h3>\r\n<strong>IIM Indore offers the following academic programmes</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Post Graduate Programme in Management (PGP), a two-year full-time residential programme equivalent to an MBA.</li>\r\n<li>Executive Post-Graduate Programme in Management (EPGP), a one-year full-time residential programme equivalent to an MBA.</li>\r\n<li>Post Graduate Programme in Management for Executives (PGPMX), a two-year alternate-weekend programme.</li>\r\n<li>Fellow Programme in Management (FPM).</li>\r\n<li>Integrated Programme in Management (IPM)  IIM Indore, a five-year integrated course in management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\nAdmission\r\nAdmissions to the flagship Post Graduate Programmes in Management (PGP) at Indore, Dubai(UAE) and Mumbai, is through the <strong>Common Admission Test (CAT)</strong> conducted by the <strong>IIMs</strong>. Non Resident Indian (NRI) candidates are also eligible to apply and should have scored a minimum <strong>GMAT</strong> score of 650 to be shortlisted for further evaluations. Admissions to the Executive Post Graduate Programme in Management (EPGP), a programme for executives with a minimum of 5 years work experience, is through the globally accepted <strong>GMAT</strong>. The candidates are shortlisted on the basis of their GMAT score, which on average has been 700 for the past batches, quality of work experience, extra-curricular record and future managerial potential. The five-year  Integrated Programme in Management (IPM) <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Integrated_Programme_in_Management_(IPM)_-_IIM_Indore" title="Integrated Programme in Management (IPM) - IIM Indore" target="_blank">Integrated Programme in Management (IPM) - IIM Indore</a>, the first of its kind in India launched by IIM Indore, is a unique and creative programme to meet the aspirations of young students to become management professionals, change agents and societal leaders\r\n\r\n<h3>IIM Indore Was Ranked</h3>\r\n#6 by the Business Today 50 best business schools of 2012,\r\n#5 by the Hindustan Times India''s top 50 business schools of 2011\r\n#8 by the 2012 edition of CNBC-TV18''s Top B-Schools in India.\r\n\r\n<strong>Address:</strong> Prabandh Shikhar, Rau Pithampur Road, Indore, Madhya Pradesh 453556\r\n<strong>Phone:</strong> 0731 243 9666\r\n<strong>Enrollment:</strong> 1,125 (2010)\r\n<strong>Founded:</strong> 1996\r\n<strong>Academic staff:</strong> 66\r\n<strong>Parent organization:</strong> Indian Institutes of Management\r\n<strong>Website: http://www.iimidr.ac.in/', 'IIM INDORE', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'iim-indore', '', '', '2016-02-15 20:00:17', '2016-02-15 20:00:17', '', 0, 'http://www.mpinformation.com/?p=383', 0, 'post', '', 0),
