(403, 1, '2016-02-15 18:53:49', '2016-02-15 18:53:49', 'With the objectives of imparting high quality management education and training, the Department of Higher Education, Ministry of Human Resource Development, Government of India established Indian Institute of Management Indore (IIM Indore) as Institution of Excellence. These Institutions are recognized as premier management institutions, comparable to the best in the world for teaching, research and interaction with industries.\r\n\r\n<h2>Established IIITM</h2>\r\nEstablished in 1996, IIM Indore is the sixth in the family of state-supported management schools. Since its inception, IIM Indore has been acting as a leader in the field of management education, interfacing with the industry, government sector and PSUs. IIM Indore is registered as a Society under Societies Registration Act, 1973.\r\n\r\nSituated atop a scenic hillock, the 193 acre campus of IIM Indore provides an ideal backdrop for contemplative learning. IIM Indore has the latest in teaching aids, rich learning resources, a strong IT backbone, state-of-the-art sports complex and hostels as well as contemporary infrastructure.', 'IIM INDORE', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '383-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-15 18:53:49', '2016-02-15 18:53:49', '', 383, 'http://www.mpinformation.com/383-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(404, 1, '2016-02-15 19:55:09', '2016-02-15 19:55:09', '<h3>History</h3>\nIIM Indore, which came into existence in 1996, was established as the sixth Indian Institute of Management after<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IIM_Calcutta" title="IIM Calcutta"  target="_blank">IIM Calcutta</a>(1961),<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IIM_Ahmedabad" title="IIM Ahmedabad" target="_blank">IIM Ahmedabad</a>(1963),<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IIM_Bangalore" title="IIM Bangalore" target="_blank">IIM Bangalore</a>(1972),<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IIM_Lucknow" title="IIM Lucknow" target="_blank">IIM Lucknow</a>(1984) and<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IIM_Kozhikode" title="IIM Kozhikode" target="_blank">IIM Kozhikode</a>(1996).The institute was the youngest among the IIM''s until 2008, when<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IIM_Shillong" title="IIM Shillong" target="_blank">IIM Shillong</a>was instituted.\n\n<h3>Academics</h3>\n<strong>IIM Indore offers the following academic programmes</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Post Graduate Programme in Management (PGP), a two-year full-time residential programme equivalent to an MBA.</li>\n<li>Executive Post-Graduate Programme in Management (EPGP), a one-year full-time residential programme equivalent to an MBA.</li>\n<li>Post Graduate Programme in Management for Executives (PGPMX), a two-year alternate-weekend programme.</li>\n<li>Fellow Programme in Management (FPM).</li>\n<li>Integrated Programme in Management (IPM)  IIM Indore, a five-year integrated course in management</li>\n</ul>\n\n\nAdmission\nAdmissions to the flagship Post Graduate Programmes in Management (PGP) at Indore, Dubai(UAE) and Mumbai, is through the <strong>Common Admission Test (CAT)</strong> conducted by the <strong>IIMs</strong>. Non Resident Indian (NRI) candidates are also eligible to apply and should have scored a minimum <strong>GMAT</strong> score of 650 to be shortlisted for further evaluations. Admissions to the Executive Post Graduate Programme in Management (EPGP), a programme for executives with a minimum of 5 years work experience, is through the globally accepted <strong>GMAT</strong>. The candidates are shortlisted on the basis of their GMAT score, which on average has been 700 for the past batches, quality of work experience, extra-curricular record and future managerial potential. The five-year  Integrated Programme in Management (IPM) <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Integrated_Programme_in_Management_(IPM)_-_IIM_Indore" title="Integrated Programme in Management (IPM) - IIM Indore" target="_blank">Integrated Programme in Management (IPM) - IIM Indore</a>, the first of its kind in India launched by IIM Indore, is a unique and creative programme to meet the aspirations of young students to become management professionals, change agents and societal leaders\n\n<h3>IIM Indore Was Ranked</h3>\n#6 by the Business Today 50 best business schools of 2012,\n#5 by the Hindustan Times India''s top 50 business schools of 2011\n#8 by the 2012 edition of CNBC-TV18''s Top B-Schools in India.\n\n<strong>Address:</strong> Prabandh Shikhar, Rau Pithampur Road, Indore, Madhya Pradesh 453556\n<strong>Phone:</strong> 0731 243 9666\n<strong>Enrollment:</strong> 1,125 (2010)\n<strong>Founded:</strong> 1996\n<strong>Academic staff:</strong> 66\n<strong>Parent organization:</strong> Indian Institutes of Management\n<strong>Website: http://www.iimidr.ac.in/', 'IIM INDORE', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '383-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-02-15 19:55:09', '2016-02-15 19:55:09', '', 383, 'http://www.mpinformation.com/383-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(405, 1, '2016-02-15 19:28:14', '2016-02-15 19:28:14', 'IIM Indore With the objectives of imparting high quality management education and training, the Department of Higher Education, Ministry of Human Resource Development, Government of India established Indian Institute of Management Indore (IIM Indore) as Institution of Excellence. These Institutions are recognized as premier management institutions, comparable to the best in the world for teaching, research and interaction with industries.\r\n\r\n<h2>Established IIITM</h2>\r\nEstablished in 1996, IIM Indore is the sixth in the family of state-supported management schools. Since its inception, IIM Indore has been acting as a leader in the field of management education, interfacing with the industry, government sector and PSUs. IIM Indore is registered as a Society under Societies Registration Act, 1973.\r\n<h3>IIM Indore Was Ranked</h3>\r\n#6 by the Business Today 50 best business schools of 2012,\r\n#5 by the Hindustan Times India''s top 50 business schools of 2011\r\n#8 by the 2012 edition of CNBC-TV18''s Top B-Schools in India.\r\n<h3>Academics</h3>\r\nIIM Indore offers the following academic programmes -\r\nPost Graduate Programme in Management (PGP), a two-year full-time residential programme equivalent to an MBA.\r\nExecutive Post-Graduate Programme in Management (EPGP), a one-year full-time residential programme equivalent to an MBA.\r\nPost Graduate Programme in Management for Executives (PGPMX), a two-year alternate-weekend programme.\r\nFellow Programme in Management (FPM).\r\nIntegrated Programme in Management (IPM) - IIM Indore, a five-year integrated course in management\r\n\r\nIIMI was ranked #6 by the Business Today 50 best business schools of 2012,[23] #5 by the Hindustan Times India''s top 50 business schools of 2011[24] and #8 by the 2012 edition of CNBC-TV18''s Top B-Schools in India.[25]\r\nSituated atop a scenic hillock, the 193 acre campus of IIM Indore provides an ideal backdrop for contemplative learning. IIM Indore has the latest in teaching aids, rich learning resources, a strong IT backbone, state-of-the-art sports complex and hostels as well as contemporary infrastructure.', 'IIM INDORE', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '383-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-15 19:28:14', '2016-02-15 19:28:14', '', 383, 'http://www.mpinformation.com/383-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
