missions to the Executive Post Graduate Programme in Management (EPGP), a programme for executives with a minimum of 5 years work experience, is through the globally accepted <strong>GMAT</strong>. The candidates are shortlisted on the basis of their GMAT score, which on average has been 700 for the past batches, quality of work experience, extra-curricular record and future managerial potential. The five-year  Integrated Programme in Management (IPM) <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Integrated_Programme_in_Management_(IPM)_-_IIM_Indore" title="Integrated Programme in Management (IPM) - IIM Indore" target="_blank">Integrated Programme in Management (IPM) - IIM Indore</a>, the first of its kind in India launched by IIM Indore, is a unique and creative programme to meet the aspirations of young students to become management professionals, change agents and societal leaders\r\n\r\n<h3>IIM Indore Was Ranked</h3>\r\n#6 by the Business Today 50 best business schools of 2012,\r\n#5 by the Hindustan Times India''s top 50 business schools of 2011\r\n#8 by the 2012 edition of CNBC-TV18''s Top B-Schools in India.', 'IIM INDORE', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '383-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-15 19:48:56', '2016-02-15 19:48:56', '', 383, 'http://www.mpinformation.com/383-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
