s in Lashkar.Regular buses leave from the MP State Bus Stand for Jhanshi (3hrs), Agra (3 hrs), Shivpuri (3 hrs), Orchha (3 hrs), Delhi (9 hrs), indore (12 hrs), Bhoapl (10 hrs), Ujjain (11 hrs). Two buses leave for Khajuraho (7-8 hrs), one in the morning and one in the evening\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>Top Places to Visit in Gwalior</h3>\r\n[gallery ids="270,271,272,262"]', 'Gwalior', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '22-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-20 06:14:37', '2016-02-20 06:14:37', '', 22, 'http://www.mpinformation.com/22-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
