(651, 1, '2016-02-20 11:05:02', '2016-02-20 11:05:02', '<h3>About Mandsour</h3>\r\nMandsaur or Mandsour is a city in the Malwa region and district of Madhya Pradesh state of central India. It is the administrative headquarters of Mandsaur District.\r\n<h4>How to Reach</h4>\r\n<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody><tr>\r\n<td width="12%"><strong>By Air</strong></td>\r\n<td width="88%">Indore Airport,<strong></strong>Indore, Madhya Pradesh is the nearest one which is located at the distance of 167 km from the Mandsaur City.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>By Train</strong></td>\r\n<td>You can easily get regular trains to Mandsaur from other major cities of the country. Railway Station Mandsaur</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>By Road</strong></td>\r\n<td>There are regular buses from other major cities of the country to Mandsaur. Bus Station:Mandsaur ,Mandsaur</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\r\n<h4>Best Time to Visit</h4>\r\nBest Time to Visit: Jan to June is the best time to visit here as the weather remains pleasant. A large number of tourists throng this place during this time.\r\n\r\n<h4>Top Attraction PLaces In Mandsaur</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Temple of Lord Pashupatinath</li>\r\n<li>Nalcha Mata Temple</li>\r\n<li>GANDHI SAGAR DAM</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Mandsaur', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'mandsaur', '', '', '2016-03-02 17:59:26', '2016-03-02 17:59:26', '', 0, 'http://www.mpinformation.com/?p=651', 0, 'post', '', 0),
