me to Visit: October to June is the best time to visit here as the weather remains pleasant. A large number of tourists throng this place during this time.', 'Satpura National Park', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '803-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-04 15:55:40', '2016-03-04 15:55:40', '', 803, 'http://www.mpinformation.com/803-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
